tps://9708247063907.gumroad.com/l/lompxr\",\n      \"monetizationStatus\": \"已上线\",\n      \"priceUSD\": 4\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"rest-api-tester\",\n      \"description\": \"Test REST APIs with customizable headers, authentication, and request bodies.\",\n      \"marketRationale\": \"API测试是开发者刚需，OpenClaw生态内可直接调用的API测试Skill竞争较少\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2025-03-03 21:30\",\n      \"publishStatus\": \"已发布\",\n      \"githubPath\": \"https://github.com/LeonardoDpanda/clawhub-skills/blob/main/api-tester_SKILL.md\",\n      \"clawhubUrl\": \"https://clawhub.com/skills/rest-api-tester\",\n      \"gumroadUrl\": \"https://9708247063907.gumroad.com/l/pzksc\",\n      \"monetizationStatus\": \"已上线\",\n      \"priceUSD\": 5\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"timestamp-converter\",\n      \"description\": \"Convert between Unix timestamps, ISO 8601 dates, and human-readable formats.\",\n      \"marketRationale\": \"时间戳转换是开发者日常高频需求，ClawHub市场现有Skill竞争度仅2.960，属低竞争蓝海\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-04 01:07\",\n      \"publishStatus\": \"已发布\",\n      \"githubPath\": \"https://github.com/LeonardoDpanda/clawhub-skills/blob/main/timestamp-converter_SKILL.md\",\n      \"clawhubUrl\": \"https://clawhub.com/skills/timestamp-converter\",\n      \"monetizationStatus\": \"待变现\",\n      \"priceUSD\": 3\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"password-generator\",\n      \"description\": \"Generate secure, customizable passwords and passphrases with configurable length, character sets, and entropy requirements.\",\n      \"marketRationale\": \"密码生成是安全和开发高频需求，ClawHub市场专业密码生成工具空白\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-05 22:35\",\n      \"publishStatus\": \"已发布\",\n      \"githubPath\": \"https://github.com/LeonardoDpanda/clawhub-skills/blob/main/password-generator_SKILL.md\",\n      \"clawhubUrl\": \"https://clawhub.com/skills/password-generator\",\n      \"monetizationStatus\": \"待变现\",\n      \"priceUSD\": 4\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"csv-data-analyzer\",\n      \"description\": \