{"type":"message","id":"3b4c9604","parentId":"17868586","timestamp":"2026-03-07T17:08:54.351Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"read:20","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Multi-Channel Notification Configuration\n# Copy this file to config/telegram_bot.conf and config/email.conf\n\n# ============================================\n# Telegram Bot Configuration\n# ============================================\n# \n# Setup Instructions:\n# 1. Open Telegram and search for \"@BotFather\"\n# 2. Send \"/newbot\" and follow instructions\n# 3. Copy the bot token (format: 123456789:ABCdefGHIjklMNOpqrsTUVwxyz)\n# 4. Send \"/start\" to your new bot\n# 5. Get your chat ID: https://api.telegram.org/bot<TOKEN>/getUpdates\n#\n# Uncomment and fill in:\n# BOT_TOKEN=\"your_bot_token_here\"\n# CHAT_ID=\"your_chat_id_here\"\n\n# ============================================\n# Email Configuration (using mail/mailx)\n# ============================================\n#\n# Setup Instructions:\n# 1. Ensure mail/mailx is installed: apt install mailutils\n# 2. Configure SMTP in /etc/mail.rc or use ssmtp/msmtp\n# 3. For Gmail, use App Password (not your main password)\n#\n# Uncomment and fill in:\n# EMAIL_TO=\"your_email@example.com\"\n# EMAIL_FROM=\"clawhub@yourdomain.com\"\n# SMTP_SERVER=\"smtp.gmail.com:587\"\n# SMTP_USER=\"your_email@example.com\"\n# SMTP_PASS=\"your_app_password\"\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772903334349}}
{"type":"message","id":"fe3acb92","parentId":"3b4c9604","timestamp":"2026-03-07T17:09:13.797Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"没有配置好的通知渠道。让我创建一个任务完成的总结报告，并写入内存文件。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"通知渠道未配置。让我创建本次batch的完成报告："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write:21","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Skill Batch 生成报告 - 2026-03-08\n\n## 执行摘要\n\n✅ **任务完成**: 成功生成并发布5个高价值Skill\n\n| 指标 | 数值 |\n|-----|-----|\n| 本次生成 | 5 个 Skills |\n| 累计生成 | 25 个 Skills |\n| GitHub推送 | ✅ 成功 |\n| ClawHub发布 | ⏭️ 待手动执行 (CLI未安装) |\n| Gumroad上架 | ⏭️ 待执行 |\n\n---\n\n## 本次生成的5个Skill\n\n### 1. csv-data-processor 💰 $5\n- **分类**: 数据处理\n- **核心价值**: 专业CSV数据处理，支持过滤、合并、转换和统计分析\n- **目标用户**: 数据分析师、开发者\n- **GitHub**: https://github.com/LeonardoDpanda/clawhub-skills/blob/main/01-csv-data-processor_SKILL.md\n\n### 2. json-schema-validator 💰 $4\n- **分类**: 开发者工具\n- **核心价值**: JSON Schema验证，详细错误报告和修复建议\n- **目标用户**: API开发者、后端工程师\n- **GitHub**: https://github.com/LeonardoDpanda/clawhub-skills/blob/main/02-json-schema-validator_SKILL.md\n\n### 3. markdown-doc-generator 💰 $6\n- **分类**: 文档工具\n- **核心价值**: 从代码自动生成Markdown文档，支持多种语言\n- **目标用户**: 开源项目维护者、技术写作人员\n- **GitHub**: https://github.com/LeonardoDpanda/clawhub-skills/blob/main/03-markdown-doc-generator_SKILL.md\n\n### 4. git-commit-assistant 💰 $4\n- **分类**: Git工具\n- **核心价值**: 智能生成规范化的commit message，支持Conventional Commits\n- **目标用户**: 开发团队、开源贡献者\n- **GitHub**: https://github.com/LeonardoDpanda/clawhub-skills/blob/main/04-git-commit-assistant_SKILL.md\n\n### 5. log-analyzer-pro 💰 $7\n- **分类**: 监控工具\n- **核心价值**: 智能日志分析，错误聚类，性能指标提取\n- **目标用户**: 运维工程师、DevOps\n- **GitHub**: https://github.com/LeonardoDpanda/clawhub-skills/blob/main/05-log-analyzer-pro_SKILL.md\n\n---\n\n## 后续行动项\n\n### 高优先级\n1. **安装ClawHub CLI**\n   ```bash\n   # 参考官方文档安装 clawhub CLI\n   # 然后执行: clawhub publish ./skills/*\n   ```\n\n2. **配置Gumroad自动发布**\n   - 编辑 `/workspace/projects/workspace/config/gumroad.env`\n   - 添加 Gumroad Access Token\n   - 运行自动发布脚本\n\n### 中优先级\n3. **配置通知渠道**\n   - Telegram Bot 配置\n   - Email SMTP 配置\n\n4. **创建Skill演示页面**\n   - 为每个Skill生成示例截图/录屏\n   - 发布到社交媒体\n\n---\n\n## 市场覆盖分析\n\n本次5个Skill覆盖的类别:\n- 📊 数据处理: 1个\n- 🔧 开发者工具: 2个  \n- 📝 文档工具: 1个\n- 📦 Git工具: 1个\n- 🔍 监控工具: 1个\n\n定价策略:\n- 基础工具 ($4): 2个\n- 标准工具 ($5-6): 2个\n- 高级工具 ($7): 1个\n- **总价值**: $26\n\n---\n\n## 技术债务\n\n1. ClawHub CLI 需要手动安装\n2. Gumroad API 需要配置访问令牌\n3. 通知渠道需要配置\n\n---\n\n生成时间: 2026-03-08 01:08 (Asia/Shanghai)","file_path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/memory/skill-batch-2026-03-08.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"kimi-k2-5-260127","usage":{"input":590,"output":951,"cacheRead":31488,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33029,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772903334351}}
